    Create random groups

    Load MassLynx complete summary file

    ras.loadFile.Rd

    Asks the user for a source file and loads it with readr::read_lines().

    Usage

    ras.loadFile(sourceFile)

    Arguments

    sourceFile

    A file path

    Value

    A list of all lines in source file with "END" appended as the last line

    See also

    Other SplitOutput: ras.SplitOutput(), ras.cleanDF(), ras.splitDataLines(), ras.writeFiles()

    Examples

    dataLines = ras.loadFile(sourceFile = system.file("extdata",
                                                  "Example_MLOutput.txt",
                                                  package = "aquaras",
                                                  mustWork = TRUE))
